{"tid":1472310,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[注意]抗爭模式要改，請睇曬先留言","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T02:03:02.000Z","uid":110332,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5e600f8642690907ed80d885d592d72d99357d3a","tid":1472310,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分別講下和理非同勇武兩方面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n和理非<br />\n機場長期有人留守，取消航班當然好，就算唔夠人，都可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和你飛</span></span>，向世界各地嘅人做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">重點</span></span><br />\n去得嘅人緊記，自己係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非</span></span>死都唔會衝！你嘅主要目的係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣！唔係齋靜坐！</span></span></span>，星期日六日人多癱瘓到機場就癱，唔得就算！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好被慫恿，唔洗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉鬼</span></span>！當大多數人明就唔會俾佢慫勇到，到時佢自己攞黎7</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武<br />\n現在開始做得勇武<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">唔洗再明刀明槍！</span></span>唔怕留血！唔怕死！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亦都唔怕雙手沾上狗血</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">重點</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">休班狗最驚被一小隊示威者係冇事先係網上吹雞既情況下快閃襲擊</span></span>，雖然狗隊會儘量透過CCTV, 現場/受害者身上遺漏皮屑/汗 &amp; 口水等體液/衣物纖維/鞋印/指模/毛髮等黎破案<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但</span></span>最怕一連一百幾十單，到時有證據都冇人手。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係時候到我地製造黑色恐怖俾佢地，真正做到以眼還眼！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">總結</span></span><br />\n所有人一定要知道林奠一早冇權話事，依家嘅政府就係中共！所以佢係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定唔會</span></span>應承五大訴求！中共好驚出老解！所以先派公安，武警入狗隊！！代表咩？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗隊已經係政府最後防線！</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">爭取五大訴求先，必先破警隊，所以我哋從來沒有失焦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n和理非同勇武一定要通力合作，和理非嘅文宣方向一定要係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警察等於黑社會，社會害蟲，相反話示威者，除暴安良，為民除害，天經地義</span></span><br />\n<br />\n知己知彼，百戰百勝，請詳讀以下post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460251</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港必勝！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後為我之前出post嘅垃圾標題道歉！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對唔住</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求幫手推推</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50e2d98fbc628fd14e05fc4641197fc03cba2ca","tid":1472310,"uid":119283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:14:47.000Z","msg":"我唔敢用道德去評你對還是錯，但我100%認同你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffc6c9f042e663785ad6d23114789428be7ff06","tid":1472310,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"feedb4ccf5a2c340a8e40d2157b165562ac131ff","tid":1472310,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c50e2d98fbc628fd14e05fc4641197fc03cba2ca","tid":1472310,"uid":119283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:14:47.000Z","msg":"我唔敢用道德去評你對還是錯，但我100%認同你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"幫手推下！香港人要進化！"},{"pid":"739856af221ea423812ce47992398a0c0f786c51","tid":1472310,"uid":21139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"從今日開始，稱呼和理非及勇武者為「手足」"},{"pid":"b4f3ee19959d826dc16beb44b6a3af10316afd6b","tid":1472310,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"斬狗首不割"},{"pid":"755adb49a084df59016647756da197c4b6eeb348","tid":1472310,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"739856af221ea423812ce47992398a0c0f786c51","tid":1472310,"uid":21139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"從今日開始，稱呼和理非及勇武者為「手足」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"斬狗首不割"},{"pid":"4c7a22dffa5eb5c5490da33139b914059e052947","tid":1472310,"uid":110332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"739856af221ea423812ce47992398a0c0f786c51","tid":1472310,"uid":21139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"從今日開始，稱呼和理非及勇武者為「手足」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:54:34.000Z","msg":"我一向都叫手足"},{"pid":"a1b54c08bf13d34a1cb855211ce6f4e4b54a0f78","tid":1472310,"uid":260766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"講中心底話，大力推"},{"pid":"b6237858c8b5b864701a462be07a6653b2682ebf","tid":1472310,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"斬狗首不割"},{"pid":"0a65891c701820f89542cc323fcaee0778c8f880","tid":1472310,"uid":110332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a1b54c08bf13d34a1cb855211ce6f4e4b54a0f78","tid":1472310,"uid":260766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"講中心底話，大力推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:56:18.000Z","msg":"幫幫手！置頂！"},{"pid":"dadd37ec4364f9fef6b9cf6f4b631d2152bd7206","tid":1472310,"uid":110332,"like":1